From: Xinhui Yang <cyan@cyano.uk>
Date: Tue, 7 Apr 2026 02:50:07 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] configure: patch out SELinux support

We have no plan to maintain SELinux support for our distro.
---
 configure | 3 ---
 1 file changed, 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/configure b/configure
index 7437db4..27f5714 100755
--- a/configure
+++ b/configure
@@ -594,9 +594,6 @@ check_setns
 echo -n "libc has name_to_handle_at: "
 check_name_to_handle_at
 
-echo -n "SELinux support: "
-check_selinux
-
 echo -n "libtirpc support: "
 check_tirpc
 
